resonators","count":1},{"word":"pity","count":1},{"word":"city","count":1},{"word":"built","count":1},{"word":"disruptor","count":1},{"word":"rules","count":1},{"word":"assure","count":1},{"word":"act","count":1},{"word":"shadows","count":1},{"word":"seeks","count":1},{"word":"fair","count":1},{"word":"challenge","count":1},{"word":"respect","count":1},{"word":"beg","count":1},{"word":"witness","count":1},{"word":"birth","count":1},{"word":"new","count":1},{"word":"escorting","count":1},{"word":"ephor","count":1},{"word":"ends","count":1},{"word":"march","count":1},{"word":"onward","count":1},{"word":"creations","count":1},{"word":"await","count":1},{"word":"comes","count":1},{"word":"skills","count":1},{"word":"action","count":1},{"word":"happy","count":1},{"word":"hunter's","count":1},{"word":"den","count":1},{"word":"busiest","count":1},{"word":"encampment","count":1},{"word":"across","count":1},{"word":"sanguis","count":1},{"word":"plateaus","count":1},{"word":"hunter","count":1},{"word":"passes","count":1},{"word":"setting","count":1},{"word":"heh","count":1},{"word":"priestess's","count":1},{"word":"words","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"merit","count":1},{"word":"blessings","count":1},{"word":"forever","count":1},{"word":"sacrifices","count":1},{"word":"excuse","count":1},{"word":"taking","count":1},{"word":"permission","count":1},{"word":"accompany","count":1},{"word":"request","count":1},{"word":"bold","count":1},{"word":"dangers","count":1},{"word":"ahead","count":1},{"word":"warrior","count":1},{"word":"cannot","count":1},{"word":"simply","count":1},{"word":"gladiators","count":1},{"word":"united","count":1},{"word":"defenders","count":1},{"word":"claim","count":1},{"word":"ask","count":1},{"word":"heart","count":1},{"word":"earned","count":1},{"word":"deeds","count":1},{"word":"today","count":1},{"word":"reflect","count":1},{"word":"greatness","count":1},{"word":"wastelands","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"imagined","count":1},{"word":"four","count":1},{"word":"years","count":1},{"word":"circumstances","count":1},{"word":"command","count":1},{"word":"deploy","count":1},{"word":"stones","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"personally","count":1},{"word":"perimeter","count":1},{"word":"stays","count":1},{"word":"undisturbed","count":1},{"word":"hurry","count":1},{"word":"sovereign's","count":1},{"word":"begins","count":1},{"word":"amusing","count":1},{"word":"seek","count":1},{"word":"ruler","count":1},{"word":"strong","count":1},{"word":"lead","count":1},{"word":"pliable","count":1},{"word":"led","count":1},{"word":"luck","count":1},{"word":"needle","count":1},{"word":"sea","count":1},{"word":"position","count":1},{"word":"i'd","count":1},{"word":"keep","count":1},{"word":"mouth","count":1},{"word":"shut","count":1},{"word":"falls","count":1},{"word":"ambitions","count":1},{"word":"entered","count":1},{"word":"choice","count":1},{"word":"demanded","count":1},{"word":"shed","count":1},{"word":"blade","count":1},{"word":"wielded","count":1},{"word":"proof","count":1},{"word":"loyalty","count":1},{"word":"entertainment","count":1},{"word":"lords","count":1},{"word":"reconsider","count":1},{"word":"alliance","count":1},{"word":"hollow","count":1},{"word":"figures'","count":1},{"word":"influence","count":1},{"word":"judging","count":1},{"word":"behavior","count":1},{"word":"corrupted","count":1},{"word":"mind","count":1},{"word":"far","count":1},{"word":"entrance","count":1},{"word":"mesona","count":1},{"word":"nearby","count":1},{"word":"helped","count":1},{"word":"companions","count":1},{"word":"resist","count":1},{"word":"corruption","count":1},{"word":"paid","count":1},{"word":"pride","count":1},{"word":"former","count":1},{"word":"death","count":1},{"word":"free","count":1},{"word":"torment","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"promise","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"worry","count":1},{"word":"illusion","count":1},{"word":"wall","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"I am Gladiator Avidius. At your service.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"\"Gladiating\" and \"hunting\" are the very pillars upon which the glory of Septimont stands. I believe no Gladiator would refuse such an honor if invited.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"I, of course, am no exception.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Please, if you'll follow me. Honored guest from afar.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Good day to you, {Male=Sir;Female=Madam} {PlayerName}. It seems you too have taken an interest in the Temple's murals.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"They are the works of past Priestesses. They depict prophecies glimpsed in the <te href=750009>Sacred Flames</te>—ones already fulfilled and ones yet to come.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"In any case, all these murals point to two prophecies of importance.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"The first is a Ragunnesi prophecy condemning Septimont's lack of faith in the Sentinel—","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"\"Hear this, O faithless ones of Septimont. The Divinity of the high heavens has grown enraged. Should your monarch once more stand in contempt of Their will, annihilation shall be your fate.\"","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"The second is a continuation of the Ragunnesi prophecy, delivered by Septimont's Priestesses—","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"\"Only the Hero of Heroes of extraordinary power, risen from the dark tides, shall bring eternity to Septimont. Then shall the waters quiet, the tempest still, and glory return with the blood of the old king.\"","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"You seem drawn to that particular mural... It tells of a calamity yet to come, and as always, the Hero of Heroes who shall rise among us to turn the tide of fate.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Yet the identity of this Hero remains a mystery. Coincidentally, much like the absent part of this mural, the prophecy of our victory over the coming disaster remains untold...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Whether the Priestesses can't foresee the fate that awaits, or whether the true prophecy is meant to remain hidden... Is indeed a question worth pondering.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"I happened to wander by, passing the time as one does. No need to trouble yourself with someone as inconsequential as I, Priestess.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Isn't paying respects to the Heroes fairly commonplace? Surely, we needn't allow rivalry to come between us, Priestess.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Please, I don't deny that I am ambitious and aspire to better my station. But I value my duty to defend Septimont's glory just as equally.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Should I become the next Hero, Septimont would be spared when the next calamity arrives. Is this not what the Tetragon Temple has prophesized?","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"She possesses many qualities worthy of a Hero. But she lacks the \"extraordinary power\" mentioned in the prophecy.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"As a Resonator, Augusta offers nothing special. Yet throughout Septimont's history, every Hero of Heroes was born with extraordinary gifts.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"She may have the strength to wield a sword, but I doubt her ability to endure pain and the slow, wearisome passage of time like other Resonators.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"It's a pity that in a city built on prophecy, Augusta is a disruptor of the rules.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"I assure you, Priestess, I will not act from the shadows. If Augusta seeks a fair challenge, I shall honor her with the respect she deserves.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Priestess, {PlayerName}, I beg your leave.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Perhaps... we will bear witness to the birth of a new Hero in the hunt to come.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"The pleasure of escorting you to the Ephor has been fulfilled. For now, my duty ends here.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"From here, we march onward to the hunting grounds, where the Dark Tide's creations may await us. When the time comes, it will be a true pleasure to see your skills in action.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Happy hunting.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"The Hunter's Den. The busiest Gladiator encampment across the Sanguis Plateaus. Nearly every hunter passes through here on their way to the hunting grounds.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"We will rest here before setting off for the next hunt.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Heh, the Priestess's words are not without merit. I am well aware that I stand under blessings, and will forever remember the sacrifices of the Temple.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Now if you'll excuse me. I'll be taking my leave.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"As you wish, Your Excellency.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Your Excellency.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"With your permission, I wish to accompany you to Murmurstown.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"I know this request may seem bold, and I'm aware of the dangers ahead. But as a warrior of Septimont, I cannot simply stand by.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"Gladiators, we are united as defenders of Septimont's honor.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"I do not claim the right to ask this of you, but in my heart, I believe everyone here has earned the glory we bear. Let our deeds today reflect that greatness.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000001},{"text":"The Wastelands...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"I never imagined that after four years, I would return to this place under such circumstances...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"Your command is our duty, Your Excellency. We will deploy Anchor Stones around Murmurstown, and I'll personally see that the perimeter stays undisturbed.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"Please hurry, everyone. The Anchor Stone must be in place before the Sovereign's hunt begins.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"Is that so? Perhaps you'd like to remind me, my lord.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"How very amusing, Lord Falco.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"You seek a ruler strong enough to lead, yet pliable enough to be led. You'd have better luck finding a needle in the sea.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"Were I in your position, I'd keep my mouth shut. If Septimont falls, so will your ambitions.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"And allow me to remind you: I entered Manes Deep because I had no other choice, and my duty as a Gladiator demanded it.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"The blood I shed, the blade I wielded—these were proof of loyalty, not entertainment for the lords. If that's how you see it... then perhaps it is I who should reconsider this alliance.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"...He may be under the Hollow Figures' influence. Judging by his behavior, the Dark Tide has already corrupted his mind.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"The Anchor Stone is nearly in place. Sir Hercle, would you please take Lord Falco to rest?","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"This isn't far from the entrance to Manes Deep. I remember finding Mesona nearby. It's an herb that helped my companions and me resist the Dark Tide's corruption.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"...Lord Falco has paid for his pride. But as a former hero, he deserves a death free from the Dark Tide's torment.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"I will do what I can to help...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"Sir Hercle, please look after him. I'll bring the herb back.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"I promise it won't take long. Don't worry.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"...How could it be...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"No... It must be the Dark Tide's illusion...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"This wall... No, it can't be...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"...","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002}]}